                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt mr-2"></i>Total Moderators: 24
